• Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - 702 host Eusebius McKaiser hosted a forum that examines, discusses and debates the theme The Negotiated Settlement. His guests included former Finance Minister Pravin Gordhan, Roelf Meyer, Ranjeni Munusamy and Febe Potgieter-Gqubule. The panel unpacked Nelson Mandela's legacy in the context of South Africa today. eNCA